OL,4,G1400FMurder She Wrote
OL,5,     GJessica has to unravel the
OL,6,     Gsecrets and threats at the
OL,7,     Gfuneral of a friend in Wyoming.
OL,8,G1500FMurder She Wrote
OL,9,     GA letter from an old friend
OL,10,     Gbrings Jessica to a luxury island
OL,11,     Ghotel, where she arrives just in
OL,12,     Gtime to investigate the sender's
OL,13,     Gmurder.
OL,14,G1600FMurder She Wrote
OL,15,     G...Possibly. Tempers flare in
OL,16,     GCabot Cove over the planned
OL,17,     Gconstruction of a hotel, and a
OL,18,     Gtycoon with many enemies is found
OL,19,     Gdead on the building site of his
OL,20,     Ghigh-rise hotel.
