OL,4,G2000FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,5,     GIn 1944, U.S. forces fought a
OL,6,     Gbrutal battle to seize a coral
OL,7,     Gisland in the Kwajalein Atoll
OL,8,     Gfrom entrenched Japanese troops,
OL,9,     Gsecuring a vital South Pacific
OL,10,     Gmilitary base.
OL,11,G2030FBattlefront: WWII Road to Victory
OL,12,     GAs the United States prepared for
OL,13,     Gthe invasion of the Philippines,
OL,14,     Gscheduled for late 1944, the tiny
OL,15,     GPalau Islands had to be taken
OL,16,     Gfirst.
